---
title: Classic Chicken & Dill-Parsley Burger with Caramelised Onion & Fries
description: Bring a little flair to burger night by using classic flavours such as caramelised onion, Aussie spice blend and dill-parsley mayo to turn a tender chicken fillet into a filling supreme burger.

